        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="data-on-eks-blogs--benchmarks">Data on EKS Blogs &amp; Benchmarks<a class="hash-link" href="#data-on-eks-blogs--benchmarks" title="Direct link to heading">â€‹</a></h2><p>In this section you will find <code>Blogs</code> and <code>Benchmark reports</code> for the following topics.</p><p>AWS Data Analytics and ML blogs are featured a short blogs.</p><p>ðŸš€ <a href="https://docs.aws.amazon.com/emr/latest/EMR-on-EKS-DevelopmentGuide/emr-eks.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">EMR on EKS</a></p><p>ðŸš€ <a href="https://spark.apache.org/docs/latest/running-on-kubernetes.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Spark on EKS</a></p><p>ðŸš€ Custom Kubernetes Schedulers (e.g., <a href="https://yunikorn.apache.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Apache YuniKorn</a>, <a href="https://volcano.sh/en/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Volcano</a>)</p><p>ðŸš€ Job Schedulers (e.g., <a href="https://airflow.apache.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Apache Airflow</a>, <a href="https://argoproj.github.io/argo-workflows/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Argo Workflows</a>)</p><p>ðŸš€ Distributed Databases (e.g., <a href="https://cassandra.apache.org/_/blog/Cassandra-on-Kubernetes-A-Beginners-Guide.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Cassandra</a>, <a href="https://github.com/cockroachdb/cockroach-operator" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">CockroachDB</a>, <a href="https://github.com/mongodb/mongodb-kubernetes-operator" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">MongoDB</a> etc.)</p><p>ðŸš€ Streaming Platforms (e.g., <a href="https://github.com/apache/kafka" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Apache Kafka</a>, <a href="https://github.com/apache/flink" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Apache Flink</a>, Apache Beam etc.)</p>]]></content>
